{"tid":707301,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【正人渣系列-超冇風度】唔肯開門唔肯排隊 吳嘉龍當女友係阿四","createTime":"2018-06-18T14:20:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-20T04:39:24.000Z","uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f1ee076ed044f7a89eacbb619da590fd7966b1d5","tid":707301,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:20:51.000Z","msg":"吳耀漢囝囝吳嘉龍出名花弗，不過自從識咗圈外女友後定性咗好多，近年感情相當穩定，只係間唔中被影到兩個喺街頭耍吓花窗。早前吳嘉龍同女友現身中環，未知係咪同女友一齊太耐冇晒新鮮感，吳嘉龍全程大少爺上身，唔幫女友開門，連買嘢食都要女友代勞！雖然吳大少生得有型，但咁冇風度，小心俾女撇呀！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LpBq-Q00zbs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLpBq-Q00zbs&d=DEPrfqq5BVsZqc%2FvWm%2F6rARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=f87b2432\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LpBq-Q00zbs</a>"},{"pid":"130903401c4dc1fba02b2f9e0d106897e3a01e4c","tid":707301,"uid":71166,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:23:37.000Z","msg":"佢女友好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20161112/photo/1112-00282-012v1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20161112%2Fphoto%2F1112-00282-012v1.jpg&h=ba5a5072&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160101/photo/bkn-20160101062830133-0101_00862_001_01b.jpg?20160102044225\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20160101%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20160101062830133-0101_00862_001_01b.jpg%3F20160102044225&h=633347ee&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"34a38a4e33e33cb6f584b175d814a528b06f7342","tid":707301,"uid":85132,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"作文比賽?"},{"pid":"e1b116b835129ec3f5c67a16ed177f966c78c15e","tid":707301,"uid":71166,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">乍見滿臉血！ 港星吳耀漢帥兒當街慘遭潑漆</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">港星吳嘉龍</span>帥氣挺拔，曾演出電影《破風》、《金雞SSS》等賣座片，也曾和蔡依林（Jolin）在音樂電影《特務J》中激吻，同時他也是資深影星吳耀漢之子，昨晚卻<span style=\"color: red;\">在中環某大廈突然遭人潑紅漆，半張臉、身上皮衣滿是紅漆，乍看以為發生血案。</span><br />\n事發後，現場來了十多名警察，連救護車也到場，只見大廈門口有個麥當勞紙杯上沾有紅漆，疑似就是潑灑的容器。警方表示，事件中施襲者已遭拘捕，吳嘉龍也表示沒有與人結怨，不知為何會被潑漆，隨即坐上救護車離去。（娛樂中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20160204/640_9f611d9fe6f8a67f163b3936f2839c06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160204%2F640_9f611d9fe6f8a67f163b3936f2839c06.jpg&h=d0db2d2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20160204/640_a254af044a4727e488afa36ec140ec8c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160204%2F640_a254af044a4727e488afa36ec140ec8c.jpg&h=364753e4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dab224fa806e1cffce30e50bea1924e474c0f11","tid":707301,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34a38a4e33e33cb6f584b175d814a528b06f7342","tid":707301,"uid":85132,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"作文比賽?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-18T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"有圖都叫作文？"},{"pid":"54e5b184ba0ba07bf42b98e1109edd37dd44b4a2","tid":707301,"uid":85132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0dab224fa806e1cffce30e50bea1924e474c0f11","tid":707301,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"34a38a4e33e33cb6f584b175d814a528b06f7342","tid":707301,"uid":85132,